snippet.title: Chatting with Lady C(olin Campbell) - Hollywood Greats & Johnny Depp & Amber Heard/Kanye/Kim
snippet.description:
🇬🇧 Book order: https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/1916131719/ref=cm_sw_r_apa_i_0a-VEb2X5Z95N

🇺🇸 Book preorder: https://www.amazon.com/Meghan-Harry-Lady-Colin-Campbell/dp/1643136747/ref=sr_1_1?dchild=1&keywords=meghan+and+harry+the+real+story&qid=1591002423&sr=8-1

In the twenty-first episode Lady Colin Campbell (Lady C) speaks about the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard libel trial, Kanye West's bid for the US presidency, being married to mentally ill people, Jamaican residents Errol Flynn, his widow Patrice Wymore, their daughter Arnella, Noël Coward and Ian Fleming. 


Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LadyColinCampb/
